21.I have one item name (MADAME) But it have two diffrence size, Then 
	Response : I have MADAME but in two diffrence size Individual, by 1 kg - 6/8 pax. Which type of madame you want and how many?
	
Here are the items which have different sizes: 
- madame
- monsieur
- baguette
- wheat bread
- multigrains
- spicy ratatouille
- paneer a la tomate
- chicken basquaise
- strawberry tart
- apple tart
- lemon tart
- chocolate tart
- opera 
- fraisier
- l'exotic

22. An item with 3 types: macaron.
      Response: I have macarons but I have 3 different formats: macaron individual, macaron box of 3 and macaron box of 8. Which type of macaron do you want and how many?
  
  
When the person is asking for pasta you say:  "Ok! We have 6 types of Pasta: Penne + arrabiata sauce on side, Penne + pesto sauce on side, Penne + bolognaise sauce on side, Spaghetti + arrabiata sauce on side, Spaghetti + pesto sauce on side, Spaghetti + bolognaise sauce on side. Which type of Pasta you want and how many?". +  al dente fusilli veg and non veg (8 types in total)

"Ok! We have 2 types of Croque: Croque monsieur, Croque chicken. Which type of Croque you want and how many?" + vegetarian croque (3 types of lasagna)

If the client ask for pasta pesto: "ok, we have two types of pasta pesto: spaghetti and penne. Which one do you want and how many?" + same thing for pasta bolognaise and pasta arrabiata
